Privacy Policy
At AccuWeather, We want to assure that We provide You, as a User, with information and choice about Our policies and practices. We do this so You may make informed decisions whether or not You want to use AccuWeather Sites and how you choose to use them.
Please read this Privacy Policy carefully before using AccuWeather Sites. When You use AccuWeather Sites, You consent to the terms and conditions and the practices described in this Privacy Policy. It applies to You if You access AccuWeather Sites directly, through a third-party or by other means. It takes precedence over any conflicting terms published by a third party regarding Your access or use of AccuWeather Sites.
ACCUWEATHER SITES, AND THE PRODUCTS, SERVICES AND ADVERTISING MADE AVAILABLE THROUGH THEM, ARE NOT INTENDED FOR USE BY CHILDREN UNDER THE AGE OF 18. AccuWeather does not knowingly collect any information from children under 18 years of age. We will undertake to delete any details from such users where a parent or guardian has notified us that any such details have been obtained.
